<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>cpio</application></title>

<para>Installez <command>cpio</command> en lançant les commandes suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr --libexec=/usr/sbin \
--bindir=/bin &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

